{"tid":111241,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［真係好痕 有圖］皮膚劃痕症點醫好","createTime":"2017-02-07T09:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T09:43:55.000Z","uid":38353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3a8c7097f172e090c6612e1882b2251e887e32","tid":111241,"uid":38353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"呢個病困擾左我好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我中二果時出過一次好勁嘅蕁麻疹（全身皮膚，面部）。好返之後就得到呢個病，每一次有創傷，就會跟著創嘅位置出現痕條，想睇下巴絲有冇人對呢個病有認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過Google都唔知有嗱辦法適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7yL8fZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7yL8fZ.jpg&h=cd93f909&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/07/173151_ec0e2aafa684d680346fc967db849095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2F173151_ec0e2aafa684d680346fc967db849095.jpg&h=6748afcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dd1d0cee416b472deac63f060d868704a33099e","tid":111241,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:28:44.000Z","msg":"我都有，一路都搞唔掂，慢慢發現天氣一轉就仆街"},{"pid":"aafb47bb9dbdf44bd10fe1783a67c610917af73c","tid":111241,"uid":38353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都有，一路都搞唔掂，慢慢發現天氣一轉就仆街</blockquote><br />\n都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb29926589ade9b297e40ae0b4f80f5f4946c4b","tid":111241,"uid":69098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:43:54.000Z","msg":"仲以為得我會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想知原因<br />\n小學都係試過有皮膚病(唔記得咩事)<br />\n之後就一r痕就會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e4f16b3e5e083889d3da833f9ecc45170cabb3","tid":111241,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都有，一路都搞唔掂，慢慢發現天氣一轉就仆街</blockquote><br />\n都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我以前睇咗幾個月中醫，話濕，食啲藥屙到我仆街，但又照痕，屌"},{"pid":"144cf5cb997f16af2905262f377fe7d979cbdcd1","tid":111241,"uid":48330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"我都係咁, 不過無為意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d75ffccdba06a540ba3fa9a814a57b5a8748a9","tid":111241,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢幾日痕到傻仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ec493f2f1b1931fae35fe0519077923ebeb8c6","tid":111241,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以為得我會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想知原因<br />\n小學都係試過有皮膚病(唔記得咩事)<br />\n之後就一r痕就會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚴重起上嚟可以用指甲劃寫字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3df9fa4bca29a60c971f407318c22bb3235f368","tid":111241,"uid":69098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲以為得我會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想知原因<br />\n小學都係試過有皮膚病(唔記得咩事)<br />\n之後就一r痕就會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n